<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="row align-items-center">

        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h1 class="fw-bold display-5">
                Manage Courses & Feedback Effortlessly 🚀
            </h1>

            <p class="text-muted mt-3">
                A modern platform where students can register for courses 
